====test====
Given form data expected in request body then return 422 when that body is invalid.
====spec====
openapi: '3.0.1'
paths:
  /path:
    post:
      responses:
        200:
          schema:
            type: string
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/x-www-form-urlencoded:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                reserved:
                  type: string
            encoding:
              reserved:
                contentType: text/plain
                allowReserved: false
====server====
mock -p 4010
====command====
curl -i -X POST http://localhost:4010/path -H "Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded" --data-urlencode "reserved=:/?#[]@!$&'()*+,;"
====expect====
HTTP/1.1 422 Unprocessable Entity
content-type: application/problem+json
Connection: keep-alive

{"tobe": "done"}